                           <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_I_1274"><add>anstatt</add></roleName></rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="pe__agnes_QGW_II_I_1274">Agnes, seine <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__niklas_roitner_QGW_II_I_1274">Hausfrau</roleName><roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_I_1274"><add>anstatt</add></roleName></rs></rs>, <triggerstring n="disp">bestätigen, dass
                     sie</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">mit Erlaubnis</triggerstring> des <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org" ref="org__krems">Bürgermeisters
                           und des Rathes</rs></rs></rs> 4 lb dn. <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">anstatt</triggerstring> ihrer <rs type="person" ref="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_I_1274"><roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__niklas_roitner_QGW_II_I_1274">Brudertochter</roleName> Margreten, <rs type="person" ref="pe__stephan_roitner_QGW_II_I_1274">Steffleins des Roitner</rs>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__stephan_roitner_QGW_II_I_1274">tochter</roleName></rs></rs> , <triggerstring n="disp">eingenommen haben, und
                     verpfänden dafür</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">mit Handen</triggerstring> ihres <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_an_dem_ekk_QGW_II_I_1274"><roleName type="title">Burgherrn</roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Niclas an dem Ekk, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__krems-dominikaner">subprior</roleName> des
                        convencz Predigerordens ze Chrems</rs></rs> , ihr Haus, gelegen ze Chrems in
                  der Ledergassen zwischen Weipocz haus, des ledrer, und Georgins des Olm paider
                  häuser, <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_1274_men_1">von dem man 18 dn. zu Burgrecht und in das
                     genannte Kloster 1 lb dn. ze dinst dient</rs>.</rs></p></div><div type="nota"><p/></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>